00:21:30.780 --> 00:21:32.480 align:middle line:10%
One of the interesting
things about Bhakti

00:21:32.480 --> 00:21:36.280 align:middle line:10%
is that all of the
forms of Ishwar

00:21:36.280 --> 00:21:40.900 align:middle line:10%
are accompanied by
a female consort.

00:21:40.900 --> 00:21:45.165 align:middle line:84%
So Shiva and Parvati,
Lakshmi and Narayana,

00:21:45.165 --> 00:21:47.680 align:middle line:90%
and Radha Krishna and Sitaram.

00:21:47.680 --> 00:21:49.950 align:middle line:84%
So Godhead, then in
the Bhakti traditions,

00:21:49.950 --> 00:21:54.300 align:middle line:84%
is almost always
conceived of has

00:21:54.300 --> 00:21:58.860 align:middle line:84%
a complimentary pair, who are
two, but one, at the same time.

00:21:58.860 --> 00:22:06.860 align:middle line:10%
On the path of Bhakti there
is the lover and the beloved.

00:22:06.860 --> 00:22:10.900 align:middle line:84%
And we understand that
there is no more powerful

00:22:10.900 --> 00:22:17.140 align:middle line:84%
force in all of the spiritual
or material existence than love.

00:22:17.140 --> 00:22:21.560 align:middle line:84%
So there's this love affair
at the center all existence.

00:22:21.560 --> 00:22:23.590 align:middle line:90%
How beautiful is that?

00:22:23.590 --> 00:22:27.580 align:middle line:84%
Not some kind of
void or nothingness,

00:22:27.580 --> 00:22:31.310 align:middle line:84%
but a love affair at the
very center of existence.

00:22:31.310 --> 00:22:33.210 align:middle line:90%
And we're part of that.

00:22:33.210 --> 00:22:37.975 align:middle line:84%
The real story is that every
soul is united to the Supreme

00:22:37.975 --> 00:22:39.650 align:middle line:90%
like a bride.

00:22:39.650 --> 00:22:43.110 align:middle line:84%
Every one of us is the
beloved of the Supreme One.

00:22:43.110 --> 00:22:48.420 align:middle line:10%
Because soul not
Indian and not Western.

00:22:48.420 --> 00:22:49.790 align:middle line:10%
Soul is the soul.

00:22:49.790 --> 00:22:54.610 align:middle line:10%
And soul and God is a very,
very, very good connection.

00:22:54.610 --> 00:22:55.780 align:middle line:90%
Always.

00:22:55.780 --> 00:23:00.830 align:middle line:84%
Just like a snowflake, that
each and every snowflake is

00:23:00.830 --> 00:23:04.070 align:middle line:90%
individual, unique, and sacred.

00:23:04.070 --> 00:23:08.450 align:middle line:84%
And that each one of us
in our intrinsic identity

00:23:08.450 --> 00:23:12.800 align:middle line:90%
is unique, sacred, personal.

00:23:12.800 --> 00:23:22.260 align:middle line:90%
[NON-ENGLISH CHANTING]

00:23:22.260 --> 00:23:26.480 align:middle line:84%
If you have love, even though
the Lord is unattainable,

00:23:26.480 --> 00:23:28.820 align:middle line:90%
like so many [NON-ENGLISH].

00:23:28.820 --> 00:23:30.720 align:middle line:84%
All the devas are
trying to find them,

00:23:30.720 --> 00:23:32.530 align:middle line:90%
but they can't find the end.

00:23:32.530 --> 00:23:36.210 align:middle line:84%
But if you have love and
devotion, then that one who's

00:23:36.210 --> 00:23:40.360 align:middle line:84%
unattainable, who is
beyond name, beyond form,

00:23:40.360 --> 00:23:43.790 align:middle line:84%
the essence of the Vedas,
who has become everything,

00:23:43.790 --> 00:23:50.427 align:middle line:84%
but is under the influence of
his bhaktas, of his followers.

00:23:50.427 --> 00:23:51.760 align:middle line:84%
PRANADA COMTOIS: There
is a certain type

00:23:51.760 --> 00:23:56.750 align:middle line:84%
of love that is only for God, a
selfless love and a whole love

00:23:56.750 --> 00:24:00.750 align:middle line:84%
and a fully-giving yourself
love that's only for God.

00:24:00.750 --> 00:24:07.910 align:middle line:84%
And I mistook that love for
being appropriate for men.

00:24:07.910 --> 00:24:12.210 align:middle line:90%
And I lost personal boundaries.

00:24:12.210 --> 00:24:13.840 align:middle line:84%
And I think a lot
of women do this.

00:24:13.840 --> 00:24:17.750 align:middle line:84%
They love so wholly and so
fully, with so much heart,

00:24:17.750 --> 00:24:19.650 align:middle line:90%
they could even lose themselves.

00:24:19.650 --> 00:24:22.180 align:middle line:84%
So I've lost myself
in relationships

00:24:22.180 --> 00:24:25.620 align:middle line:84%
and have come to understand
that that selfless love is

00:24:25.620 --> 00:24:28.150 align:middle line:90%
precious and is only for God.

00:24:28.150 --> 00:24:33.300 align:middle line:84%
Not that I can't express
deep, profound love

00:24:33.300 --> 00:24:35.720 align:middle line:84%
for other human beings,
which I do feel I have

00:24:35.720 --> 00:24:37.550 align:middle line:90%
and I do express.

00:24:37.550 --> 00:24:41.340 align:middle line:84%
But there's a certain
love that is only for God

00:24:41.340 --> 00:24:45.880 align:middle line:84%
and can only be truly
reciprocated by God.

00:24:45.880 --> 00:24:53.120 align:middle line:10%
I've been 44 years practicing
Bhakti yoga every day.

00:24:53.120 --> 00:24:55.860 align:middle line:10%
Every day I can say that.

00:24:55.860 --> 00:24:57.050 align:middle line:90%
And every day it's richer.

00:24:57.050 --> 00:25:00.840 align:middle line:90%


00:25:00.840 --> 00:25:03.450 align:middle line:84%
There's just-- we have so
many ups and downs in life.

00:25:03.450 --> 00:25:08.030 align:middle line:84%
We climb hills and go through
valleys and in and out.

00:25:08.030 --> 00:25:10.570 align:middle line:84%
But I can say that
Bhakti yoga is

00:25:10.570 --> 00:25:19.700 align:middle line:84%
a shelter and a foundation
that allows one to take

00:25:19.700 --> 00:25:22.240 align:middle line:90%
these things with grace.

00:25:22.240 --> 00:25:24.220 align:middle line:90%
So it's very powerful.

00:25:24.220 --> 00:25:28.810 align:middle line:84%
It's a nugget that you
think is very small.

00:25:28.810 --> 00:25:33.550 align:middle line:84%
But it's actually a
great, great jewel.

00:25:33.550 --> 00:25:44.440 align:middle line:84%
And Bhakti is service
to God, service to man,

00:25:44.440 --> 00:25:45.795 align:middle line:90%
service to self.

00:25:45.795 --> 00:25:48.765 align:middle line:90%


00:25:48.765 --> 00:25:50.270 align:middle line:90%
It's very powerful.

00:25:50.270 --> 00:25:53.780 align:middle line:84%
Wherever you catch
a drop of it-- here,

00:25:53.780 --> 00:25:58.340 align:middle line:84%
there, anywhere-- it's very
relevant to the lives of

00:25:58.340 --> 00:26:01.026 align:middle line:90%
ordinary people like you and I.

